Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}原本只露出个口部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在它也现出了全身{\r}
