Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}当你有十只触手时 收集的海星卵数量是相当可观的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在海鳃也要冒出来分一杯羹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的动物们必须要尽量从这一年一度的盛宴中多捞些好处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因为阳光出现时 一场规模浩大的变化也将随之而来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海藻是一种海生澡类 大量的海藻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因气囊内充满了气体{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}渐渐朝海面上升{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}很快 一座海底森林就诞生了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}里头住满了各种各样的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些绿色海洋的物产 虽然在世界上是首屈一指的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是这里也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}竞争最为激烈的水域{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}绿色海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}非洲的南端{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}两个大洋在这里冲撞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在浅水区 营养丰富的水流滋养着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}茂盛的海藻森林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里头几乎什么也看不见 只能看到一个虹吸管在有规律地跳动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就是靠虹吸管来呼吸的 一只普通章鱼{\r}
