Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}章鱼动身追踪螃蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}然后潜伏起来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}耐心等待 准备伏击{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过章鱼是和大量其他捕食性动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}共同生活在好望角水域里的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海狗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还有鲨鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们全是吃章鱼的动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}前提是它们能找到章鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}睡袍鲨是下层丛林的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}猎捕专家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是时候消失了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这些皮糙肉厚的小鲨鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小到能够触达裂隙深处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过章鱼离死还远着呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把腕溜进了鲨鱼的鳃里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这样鲨鱼就无法呼吸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲨鱼只好放它离开{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只章鱼在外头的危险地带时{\r}
