Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而这件事情是我们从未记载过的{\r}
