Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}做了个防护器具用来掩蔽自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就躲在敌人的眼皮子底下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲨鱼能够闻到章鱼的气味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是贝壳却把鲨鱼给搞糊涂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这个随处可见捕食性动物的森林里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只章鱼就是靠着高人一等的才智生存下来的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海藻森林主要是在世界各地的季节性水域里繁荣生长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}特别是北美洲的太平洋沿岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这里 世界上最大的海藻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在广袤的森林里生长着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们可延伸至几百千米外的位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在某些地方 这些巨大的植物体{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}甚至高达60米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些海藻形成的植丛里密布着各种生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:11:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的生存空间和食物竞争非常激烈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这对这只美国红雀鲷来说是一大挑战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它精心照料着自己的海藻地盘{\r}
