Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和大多数农民一样 它也是一天到晚忙个不停{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些蜗牛和食草动物会来吃它的海藻{\r}
