Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的刺毛和针一样锋利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只雀鲷一定要想方设法把它弄走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但问题是海胆的数量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}变得越来越多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}等夜幕降临 光线变弱时 它就得收手了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它不仅需要休息 它还需要躲起来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因为在夜间 捕食动物会在这些森林里穿梭觅食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}电鳐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}能用45伏的电压把猎物电晕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雀鲷躲起来时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海胆们就能够肆无忌惮地吃海藻了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}阳光再次照进海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它发现自己的农田又遭到了破坏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海胆和蝗虫一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}往往蜂拥而至{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这会带来灾难性的后果 损失惨重的不仅仅是雀鲷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还有海藻森林本身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}所有植物现在都遭到了破坏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海胆在森林中四处游动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}穿过海藻田{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}留下的却是大片的不毛之地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}北美洲太平洋沿岸的许多海藻森林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都被这些成群出没的海胆糟蹋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过好在帮手就在附近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海獭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他水獭大多是在陆地上生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只有海獭常年生活在水里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}刚出生的小海獭还不太会游泳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了能让它浮起来 它的母亲花了好几个小时帮它理毛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过为了能让孩子吃到母乳 并为自己保暖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它每天吃的食物重量必须达到自身体重的30％才行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它主要是靠水生有壳动物来增重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海胆就是海獭最喜欢吃的美食之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在过去 人们为了得到海獭的毛皮 大量猎杀海獭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海獭几乎濒临灭绝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海獭的数量减少后 很多海藻森林都被海胆破坏得寸草不生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今海獭得到了保护{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}随着海獭的数量逐渐回升{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}很多海藻森林也慢慢恢复了原貌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今 某些僻远地带{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}生活着大量的海獭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们总是成群地聚在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们已经有100多年没见到这一情形了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在澳洲阳光充沛的浅水区里生长的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不是海藻 而是海洋里唯一的开花植物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海草{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这些海洋草地中 最广阔的草地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}面积可达到八千多平方千米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}整个热带地区的海洋草地 都是由鼬鲨巡逻着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鼬鲨的身体可长至五米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们那有力的双颚能让猎物皮开肉绽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的猎物是绿海龟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}绿海龟几乎完全以海草为食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一只绿海龟每天食用的海草就多达两公斤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过它们始终不能放松警惕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}健康的绿海龟要与不断逼近的鲨鱼保持一定的距离{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲨鱼在迫使绿海龟逃离的同时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也避免了海草地遭到过度啃噬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这对我们大家都有好处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}与同面积的热带雨林相比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海草地吸收并储存的二氧化碳量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是前者的35倍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此在这场对抗气候变暖的战役中 草地和鲨鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}竟然是同一阵营的盟友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}绿色海洋里艰难的生存环境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}可能会带来深远的影响{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每年 澳洲的一块草地会发生变化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在冬季的首个满月日子前后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一支军队形成了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}过去一年 它们一直在深海区里觅食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在它们要穿过海草平原{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.78,0:24:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数以十万计的蜘蛛蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.94,0:24:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们爬到彼此身上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.26,0:25:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}形成了巨大的山丘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.26,0:25:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}绵延近百米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.34,0:25:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们并不是在求偶 也不是在产卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.98,0:25:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们来到这里是为了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}长大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.82,0:25:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和所有的螃蟹一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.30,0:25:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的身体也是包裹在坚硬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.06,0:25:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不具伸缩性的壳内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.46,0:25:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此为了长大 它们必须要破壳而出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.78,0:25:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这样硬壳底下发育的软壳就能够逐渐变大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.42,0:26:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}新壳要花上好几天时间才能变硬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.62,0:26:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的腿瘸得很厉害 所以现在还无法自如行动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.38,0:26:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}失去保护的蜘蛛蟹处境非常危险{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.46,0:26:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}短尾刺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.90,0:26:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的体型很大 体长将近达到四米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.86,0:26:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它想要抓只刚换壳的软嫩蜘蛛蟹尝尝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.66,0:26:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这样的蜘蛛蟹吃起来更省事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.02,0:27:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹们想要聚在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.38,0:27:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是经刺一搅和{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.86,0:27:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹们便四处散开了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.26,0:27:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}刚换壳的蜘蛛蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.50,0:27:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还很虚弱 无法跟上队伍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.22,0:27:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最安全的位置就是蟹群的中央{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.58,0:28:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这也是它们全聚到这里的原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.26,0:28:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹越多的地方也就越安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.58,0:28:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过大多数蜘蛛蟹都逃走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.46,0:28:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在接下来的几天内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.18,0:28:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们就要准备回到深海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.02,0:28:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}继续孤单地漫游 寻找食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.22,0:28:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这不是墓地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.18,0:29:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而是十万只蜘蛛蟹在这里成功脱下了壳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.70,0:29:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在澳洲南部的绿色海洋里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.78,0:29:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这样规模浩大的动物聚集现象特别多见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.10,0:29:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过大多数动物聚到这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.70,0:29:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是出于截然不同的原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.90,0:29:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了交配繁殖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.70,0:29:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}伞膜乌贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.06,0:29:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是世界上最大的乌贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.10,0:30:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的寿命只有一两岁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}随着澳洲的夏季渐渐接近尾声{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.62,0:30:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}伞膜乌贼现在还有最后一件事情要做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.34,0:30:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那就是找到配偶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.30,0:30:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是单单在这一个海湾内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.54,0:30:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就有十万多只雄乌贼要争夺即将到来的雌乌贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.02,0:30:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里头有一个名副其实的庞然大物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.70,0:30:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的体重大概为十公斤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.82,0:30:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}皮肤上覆满了弯弯曲曲的带状条纹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.34,0:31:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是伞膜乌贼的沟通方式{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.82,0:31:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只体型较小的雄乌贼无法与它匹敌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.66,0:31:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大块头旁边是一只受它保护的雌乌贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.70,0:31:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们俩刚刚交配完{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.66,0:31:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过其他对手还是不死心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.50,0:31:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}看来小个儿雄乌贼的希望要落空了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.94,0:31:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌乌贼紧贴着巨型乌贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.70,0:32:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}身体外圈呈现出了白色条纹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.54,0:32:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一信号是在明确地表示它不想再与巨型乌贼交配了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.50,0:32:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这正是小个儿雄乌贼需要的鼓励{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.82,0:32:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它得耍点花招才行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:33:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把身体的颜色变得柔和些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.10,0:33:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}把触须缩紧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.50,0:33:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的体型正好能够伪装成雌乌贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.98,0:33:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}巨型乌贼上当了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.86,0:33:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小个儿雄乌贼和雌乌贼一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.66,0:33:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现出白色条纹 回绝了巨型乌贼的追求{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.18,0:33:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它溜到雌乌贼的旁边{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.18,0:33:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们俩交配了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.54,0:33:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和好几只雄乌贼交配{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.10,0:34:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌乌贼便能确保后代基因的多样性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.82,0:34:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只狡猾的雄乌贼离开了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.90,0:34:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它完成了最后的行动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.26,0:34:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就算是处在体型巨大的乌贼群里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.54,0:34:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}尺寸也并不是全部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.14,0:34:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在澳洲这些绿油油的草地里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.50,0:34:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些雄性动物对后代负有更大的责任{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.42,0:34:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}草海龙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.10,0:35:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是雄性草海龙 它身上携带着宝贵的货物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在与雌性草海龙交配时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.54,0:35:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把雌性草海龙产的卵收集起来 一一粘到身体下侧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.50,0:35:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在它要离开这些海藻丛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.14,0:35:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}游往更开阔的水域{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.10,0:35:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在那里 动物苦心经营的伪装很容易被识破{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而且这里还有很多捕食性动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.06,0:36:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}草海龙父亲们就是为了这个 才甘愿冒着性命危险{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.10,0:36:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}密密麻麻的小虾团{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.46,0:36:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}糠虾 这是海龙最喜欢的食物之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.58,0:36:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们把其他海龙也引到这里来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它总算等到了这一刻 是时候让孩子们脱落了{\r}
