Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.66,0:37:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过海龙宝宝还是撑了过来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.66,0:37:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们成功地孵化出来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.94,0:37:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}草海龙父亲们回到海藻密植丛中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.02,0:37:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在密植丛中它们几乎没办法被发现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.50,0:38:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而它们的孩子则留在原地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.78,0:38:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过海龙宝定会快速长大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.38,0:38:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}与此同时 它们的周围也将环绕着理想的食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.38,0:38:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大量新出生的小鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.58,0:38:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}要在绿色海洋里开始生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.06,0:38:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中一个资源最丰富的生长地当属红树林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.58,0:38:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}红树林沿着热带地区的海岸线生长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.66,0:38:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在海陆之间形成了一道天然的保护屏障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.70,0:39:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些红树林也是全世界最富饶的森林之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.06,0:39:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在水底下 红树林的拱形气生根{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.18,0:39:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}形成了稳固的基础{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.58,0:39:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这儿有着丰富的食物供鱼宝宝食用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.94,0:39:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而错综曲折的气生根又能帮它们挡住那些经常在水道附近出没的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.42,0:39:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大鱼和其他捕食性动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.86,0:40:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过在澳洲北部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.34,0:40:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}潮水退去后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.66,0:40:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小鱼只能被迫离开它们的庇护所{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.54,0:40:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在它们很容易受到攻击{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.38,0:41:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是绿色海洋里最致命的杀手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.78,0:41:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}斑琴虾蛄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.26,0:41:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是一只身长近40厘米的雄虾蛄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.02,0:42:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它不单单是在为自己猎食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.02,0:42:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它也在为自己的配偶觅食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.86,0:42:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们俩已经厮守了20年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.14,0:42:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌虾蛄要靠雄虾蛄替它寻找食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.74,0:42:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它自己的精力则用来产卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.10,0:42:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在一个食物随处可见的世界里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.14,0:42:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这似乎是一种明智的策略{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.22,0:42:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但这也是非常危险的策略{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.90,0:43:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}要是雄性伴侣消失了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.14,0:43:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它可能会挨饿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.14,0:43:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}某样东西吸引了这只雄虾蛄的注意力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.86,0:43:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也许是诱人的气味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.22,0:43:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}或许是远处的呼唤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.90,0:43:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不管是什么原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.54,0:43:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雄虾蛄都准备离开自己的洞穴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.42,0:43:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}离开自己的终身伴侣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.46,0:44:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一个更大的洞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.02,0:44:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}失去雄性伴侣的雌虾蛄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.14,0:44:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}似乎是在发出求助信号 召唤新的雄性伴侣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.10,0:44:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌虾蛄的体型越大 产的卵也就越多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.58,0:44:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}所以雄虾蛄和它交配的话 就能得到更多的后代{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.78,0:44:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过不忠行为是要付出代价的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.86,0:44:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}伴侣体型越大 食量也就越大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.18,0:45:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海洋中生物越丰饶 竞争也就越激烈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.50,0:45:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这儿就有个绿色海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.70,0:45:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它所滋养的生物数量超过了其他所有绿色海洋的总和{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.02,0:45:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不同于红树林和海草草原{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.26,0:45:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这个绿色海洋位于远海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.50,0:45:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但它只是暂时存在 而且变化莫测{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.54,0:45:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些绿色不是生根植物的颜色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.66,0:45:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而是一团团悬浮物的颜色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.58,0:45:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数十亿个微小的浮游植物正在迅速生长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.54,0:46:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}浮游植物让这里本就丰富的食物变成了世界上数一数二的盛宴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.90,0:46:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在美洲太平洋海上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.62,0:46:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成百上千只海豚正在匆匆赶去赴宴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.82,0:46:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}赴宴的不只是它们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.90,0:46:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还有海狮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.70,0:46:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们是要前往加州蒙特雷湾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.90,0:46:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大量的海藻在那里繁殖生长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.14,0:46:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}引来了无数的浮游生物食用者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.22,0:47:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数百万只鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.34,0:47:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海豚将鱼朝着海面逼去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.94,0:47:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些鱼群在海面出现后 海鸟和海狮便趁机占便宜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.06,0:47:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们要趁其他动物到来之前抢先分一杯羹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.38,0:47:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}座头鲸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.90,0:47:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成百上千头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.14,0:48:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们每朝上方猛扑一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.30,0:48:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就往肚子里吞进达100公斤的鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.82,0:48:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这场地球上罕见的盛宴上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.86,0:48:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们食用的鱼量也是最多的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.90,0:49:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些微小的浮游生物是如此重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.74,0:49:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}几乎所有的海洋生物最终都要依赖它们才能存活下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.22,0:49:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在世界各地 几乎所有海洋生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.54,0:49:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都要靠绿色海洋才能生存下去 而不是靠蓝色海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.64,0:50:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}幕后集锦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.66,0:50:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了拍摄到海底森林的壮观景象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.58,0:50:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和生活在这里的神奇生物 《蓝色星球》团队{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.86,0:50:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}研制出了一系列专业摄影设备{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.30,0:50:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}巨型球形摄像机 是在塔状冠层上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.74,0:50:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}同时拍摄海上和海里的画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.42,0:50:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}两架最先进的延时摄影设备{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.26,0:50:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}用于加快画面的时间 以揭示林地地表不为人知的景象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.34,0:51:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过在森林里生活的所有动物中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.10,0:51:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}南非好望角水域里的动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.46,0:51:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是拍摄起来最具挑战性的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.58,0:51:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}博物学家克雷格福斯特对这里最神秘的居民{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.10,0:51:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}产生了浓厚的兴趣 它就是普通章鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.38,0:51:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些水域里生活着将近100种鲨鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.98,0:51:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但这并没有把克雷格吓倒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.94,0:51:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}过去六年来 他每天早晨都会游到这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.06,0:51:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如果你在上面发现了椭圆形小坑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.74,0:52:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那你就知道它是被章鱼杀死的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.94,0:52:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}你要是再仔细看的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.02,0:52:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那些章鱼通常就在这附近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.70,0:52:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}克雷格亲眼见过这些章鱼的古怪行径{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.86,0:52:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他让本节目的摄影师罗杰霍洛克斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.14,0:52:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一起看看自己的大发现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.22,0:52:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些动物的性格魅力当即就把罗杰迷住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.98,0:52:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}普通章鱼的个性竟然会是这么多样 亲眼看到这一幕真的是太让人吃惊了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.34,0:52:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}普通章鱼全都展现出了不同的习性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.66,0:52:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些章鱼极其害羞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.38,0:52:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些的胆子非常大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.46,0:52:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们各有各的特性 这也是我喜爱它们的原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.42,0:53:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他们花了数周时间拍摄不同的章鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.98,0:53:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最后它们终于遇上了一只特别的章鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.90,0:53:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只章鱼看上去不仅不害怕摄像机{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.10,0:53:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还愿为镜头表演一番{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.18,0:53:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就是这样冒出来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.18,0:53:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接着它就朝着三脚架底下游过去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.34,0:53:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}游到我的腿旁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.74,0:53:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}感觉很棒 真的很神奇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.86,0:53:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它很快就习惯了我们两个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.98,0:53:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}所以我们拍摄到了那些非常私密的行为{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.78,0:53:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}真是太棒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.70,0:53:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我已经观察这只章鱼好几个月了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.70,0:53:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们在海里时 它很信任我们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.30,0:53:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的行为举止就跟平时一样 感觉真的很棒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.78,0:54:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}几个月后 它们总算拍摄到了这只明星章鱼捕猎的画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.14,0:54:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是后来他们也发现了和这么多捕食性动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.10,0:54:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也就是睡袍鲨同住在一个森林里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.98,0:54:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是要面临严重的后果的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.06,0:54:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}以同等重量比例来说 这些鲨鱼比大白鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.82,0:54:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}更加肆无忌惮 更具攻击性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.66,0:54:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们就像是追踪导弹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.82,0:54:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}哪怕章鱼只是散发出一点气味 睡袍鲨都会找到它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.30,0:54:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}睡袍鲨真的把章鱼抓住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.98,0:54:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我当时就想这下完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.90,0:54:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我和这只动物相处了这么久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.54,0:54:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}眼看着它被鲨鱼攻击 我心里真的很难受{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.98,0:55:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是大家都没想到的是 它反击了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.18,0:55:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把触手放了下来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.90,0:55:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}你可以看到那些触手伸进了鳃里{\r}
